# PitchPerfect Environment Variables

# ==================================================
# AI VOCAL COACH (Powered by Anthropic Claude)
# ==================================================

# To enable AI-powered vocal coaching feedback:
# 1. Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# 2. Copy this file to .env (cp .env.example .env)
# 3. Replace 'your_api_key_here' with your actual API key
# 4. Restart the Metro bundler (npm start)

EXPO_PUBLIC_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

